title: China Arrests Youths in Halloween Costumes

description:
Police descended upon Halloween festivities in China’s big cities this week to prevent youths from dressing in costumes. Spiderman, Batman, Ninja Turtles, a Fan Bingbing look-a-like, and even a Buddha and a monk were among many who were rounded up by authorities. Even big plush toys were checked to see if they were a humans dressed in cosplay. What happened next?
